Obviously, you will need to change the database name and the user/address if you're on another server.
This is designed so that you can quickly include your tables in here that you made for permissions. This should be refreshed on every git update.

REVOKE ALL PRIVILEGES, GRANT OPTION FROM '64digits_v4'@'localhost';
GRANT SELECT , INSERT , UPDATE , DELETE , CREATE , REFERENCES , SHOW VIEW ON  `64digits_v4_db`.`blogs` TO  '64digits_v4'@'localhost';
